Title: Requires at least one member of the state liquor authority appointed by the governor to be a resident of New York city
Summary: Requires at least one member of the state liquor authority appointed by the governor to be a resident of New York city.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to requiring at least one member of the state liquor authority appointed by the governor to be a resident of New York city
